text: Jeffrey "Jeff" Birch (21 October 1927 – June 2005) was an English professional footballer who played as a winger in the Football League for York City, in non-League football for Selby Town and Scarborough, and was on the books of Sheffield United without making a league appearance. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Sportspeople from Sheffield Category:English footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Selby Town F.C. players Category:Sheffield United F.C. players Category:Scarborough F.C. players Category:York City F.C. players Category:Midland Football League players Category:English Football League players
